{"tid":1884302,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[黑人問號] Park Yoho兩房853萬沽","createTime":"2020-02-17T13:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T07:27:54.000Z","uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bdb56cb6e241a72c2c0a9be7419fcfc1ab07fe82","tid":1884302,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:42:25.000Z","msg":"一手成交紀錄冊顯示，新世界（017）元朗瑧頤19樓A2室，實用面積437方呎，2房間隔，以693萬元售出，呎價15,858元。項目開售至今共沽出241伙，共套現近13億元。<br />\n同區新地（016）Park Yoho Napoli亦錄成交，26座15樓D室，實用面積541方呎，2房間隔，今日以853.1萬元售出，呎價15,769元。"},{"pid":"b4023d6ffe9e2187f6aa741be71c9314f6f81a58","tid":1884302,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"要幾多回佣先會棄Grand Yoho要Park Yoho<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGrand Yoho兩房減逾50萬沽　業主持貨3年終蝕讓離場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1874033\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1874033</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c0415435e9de4a3ae117a334c2727165d10ed860","tid":1884302,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:43:25.000Z","msg":"個價咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ee7fb710a9796ab650523aa0054787a4f4e758","tid":1884302,"uid":57674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:50:45.000Z","msg":"咁急接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1a44ffaea3829a9a7d780c2a63c39a6eebbf91","tid":1884302,"uid":62935,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"隱世高人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔遠唔要"},{"pid":"5ccecf7884c9b183dc06f580aa71e0f2ab0000b2","tid":1884302,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4023d6ffe9e2187f6aa741be71c9314f6f81a58","tid":1884302,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"要幾多回佣先會棄Grand Yoho要Park Yoho<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGrand Yoho兩房減逾50萬沽　業主持貨3年終蝕讓離場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1874033\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1874033</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:18:08.000Z","msg":"今日又一單蝕讓, 個價可以買到地鐵站上蓋, 點解會有人買山卡拉<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情進一步打擊本港經濟，部份急需資金周轉的業主，不惜勁蝕讓賣樓。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產王勤學表示，元朗GRAND YOHO 2座中層E室，實用面積520方呎，兩房間隔，去年11月開價900萬元交吉放售單位，最終累減120萬元或13%，以780萬元沽出，呎價15,000元。原業主2016年10月以857萬元一手買入單位作收租用途，持貨3年多，現轉手賬面蝕約77萬元或約9%。<br />\n<br />\n王氏指，GRAND YOHO一手開售時吸引大量投資者入市，近期市況回落，不少投資者減價求售，現時約有80個放盤，議價幅度約3%至5%。議幅相對區內其它YOHO系列屋苑多，故不乏買家伺機入市。屋苑本月錄得6宗成交，暫屬區內成交最多的屋苑，平均呎價約15,304元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200217/RAOM7O2LEQMORZMG6GJ5RKBP4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200217%2FRAOM7O2LEQMORZMG6GJ5RKBP4U%2F&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=2c405f6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200217%2FRAOM7O2LEQMORZMG6GJ5RKBP4U%2F&h=2e171e9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200217/RAOM7O2LEQMORZMG6GJ5RKBP4U/</a>"},{"pid":"219a324bd4e0b3306661902175c3d2b1afd1fcae","tid":1884302,"uid":35941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e4bf9a935532cfdbeebc29eff8b0df6f0e2814","tid":1884302,"uid":87471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:22:33.000Z","msg":"蓋清連park yoho都燈到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6260570255ff35149958cad854f38e3bbadfc2","tid":1884302,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:23:55.000Z","msg":"回佣15個？"},{"pid":"ce7479da504